title: FULL SHOW: We Chat With Patti LaBelle, Ask Yee, Inflation, And More!
itunes:title: FULL SHOW: We Chat With Patti LaBelle, Ask Yee, Inflation, And More!
description:
Today on The Breakfast Club we join thee LEGENDARY Patti LaBelle from her HOME! We talk everything from her career to iconic house parties. Later on Yee reports the latest on inflation, in this case food prices going astronomically high. Charlamagne gives his donkey of the day and Yee helps a listener who is struggling mentally during Ask Yee. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
